+  - `python3 tools/infra_mdns_hardening.py --validate-live` exited `1` with `LIVE_VALIDATION_FAILED` because the live `/etc` drop-in is still missing
+  - `python3 tools/department-commands.py run infra` produced fresh artifact `departments/infra/artifacts/checks/20260308T173458Z-r31-run-security-audit-check-for-open-ports-ssh-config-faile.md`
+- Remaining live blocker:
+  - this session still cannot install the managed drop-in into `/etc`, and the current non-privileged live check did not expose socket ownership, so the fresh artifact remains blocked on the same host-side remediation even though the owner/PID path is now covered by tests and ready for the next visible-owner run
